title: Over/Under Rico: Week 6
text:
Back to .500 for Rico after going 6-8 (1-2 Best Bets) last week on the Over/Unders. The season record stands at 38-38-1 (9-6). The selections for Week 6 are:
Over: Broncos / Browns; Bengals / Bills; Vikings / Chiefs; Lions / Bears; Cardinals / Steelers; Packers / Chargers; Patriots / Colts.
Under: Falcons / Saints; Jets / Redskins; Texans / Jaguars; Titans / Dolphins; Seahawks / Panthers; Ravens / Niners; Eagles / Giants.
Best Bets: Lions (Over), Eagles (Under), Cardinals (Over).
League (Overs listed first): Last week: 7-7; Overall 40-36-1
